task.summary: Folders are now created in the #desktop container instead of the of the document body.

added working grid displaying data from a simple JavaScript data source
Renamed html class from markos-folder-container to markos-file-manager.
Merging of software templates are now handled by _SoftwareContainer.
Consolidated all module css in markos.css

system.json now gets loaded into a memory store with global access.
